Package: hwglabr2
Title: Collection of R functions used in the Hochwagen Lab
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Luis", "Vale Silva", email = "luisvalesilva@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut"))
Description: Complete rewrite of package "hwglabr", with a focus on using Bioconductor's
    GRanges class. The intention is mainly to analyse ChIP-seq data stored in bedGraph
    format, as produced by the lab's updated ChIP-seq analysis pipeline.
URL: https://github.com/hochwagenlab/hwglabr2
BugReports: https://github.com/hochwagenlab/hwglabr2/issues
Depends: R (>= 3.2.5)
License: MIT + file LICENSE 
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
